'''卡拉切-巴尔卡尔语'''（{{lang|ru|Къарачай-Малкъар}} /Qarachaj-Malqar/）是[[突厥语系|突厥语系]]的語言，是[[卡拉恰伊人|卡拉恰伊人]]和[[巴尔卡尔人|巴尔卡尔人]]的语言。它分为两种方言：卡拉切方言（Karachay, pronouncing /ch/ and /zh/）和巴尔卡尔方言（pronouncing /ts/ and /z/）。估计使用者有24万人。使用[[西里尔字母|西里尔字母]]书写。<ref name="Compendium of the World Languages">{{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=DWAqAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA832 |title=Compendium of the World Languages |publisher=Routledge |year=2013 |authors=George L. Campbell and Gareth King |isbn=978-1-1362-5846-6 |accessdate=23 May 2014 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801131608/https://books.google.com/books?id=DWAqAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA832 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

